.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-DEBUG" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-debug \- Diagnose the latest tracked run
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose debug [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Collect tracked scheduler state, service state, batch and service log tails, and a recommended next command. Add \-\-preflight to rerun cluster prerequisite checks.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--job\-id\fR \fIJOB_ID\fR
Tracked Slurm job id to diagnose instead of the latest recorded submission.
.TP
\fB--service\fR \fISERVICE\fR
Service whose log tail should be emphasized.
.TP
\fB--lines\fR \fILINES\fR
Number of trailing log lines to include. Default: 100.
.TP
\fB--preflight\fR
Rerun preflight and include its findings.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--squeue\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the squeue executable. Default: squeue.
.TP
\fB--sacct\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sacct executable. Default: sacct.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--scontrol\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the scontrol executable. Default: scontrol.
.TP
\fB--apptainer\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the apptainer executable. Default: apptainer.
.TP
\fB--singularity\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the singularity executable. Default: singularity.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB-v\fR, \fB--verbose\fR
Increase diagnostic verbosity; repeat for debug\-level logs.
.TP
\fB--debug\fR
Enable debug\-level diagnostics (equivalent to \-vv unless RUST_LOG is set).
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--offline\fR
Forbid SSH, remote delegation, Slurm scheduler contact, submissions, allocations, and cancels.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose debug \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose debug \-f compose.yaml \-\-preflight
hpc\-compose debug \-f compose.yaml \-\-service app \-\-lines 200
hpc\-compose debug \-f compose.yaml \-\-format json
.fi
